metadata.editComments: (I think) corrected the melody and chords but why isn't anyone interested in Lucas the Spider

When first listening to this song, this section may sound like a chorus, but it can't be a chorus because it only appears once in the song. Therefore it should be described as a post-chorus.

The V/vi chord in this section is not followed by a vi chord as it normally should be, but it still works because the VI maj7 chord that follows it still has all 3 notes of a vi triad on top.

At the end of this section, I transcribed the piano melody since the singer started speaking.
